Abstract: In this chapter, we discuss the Molecular Dynamics problem for SIMD architectures: the Connection Machine (CM-2) or the MasPar MP-1 or (MP-2). For the CM-2, you may also learn how to display output from programs graphically while the programs are running with the CM-2 framebuffer. 
